\fBOMPI_Affinity_str\fP \- Obtain prettyprint strings of processor affinity
information for this process
.SH SYNTAX
.SS C Syntax
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
#include <mpi.h>
#include <mpi\-ext.h>

